###
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/nonexistent

### Response
HTTP/1.1 404 Not Found
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "error": {
        "code": "NOT_FOUND",
        "message": "Route not found",
        "requestId": "..."
    }
}

###

### Internal error (500)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/trigger-error

### Response
HTTP/1.1 500 Internal Server Error
Content-Type: application/json
Cache-Control: no-store

{
    "error": {
        "code": "INTERNAL_ERROR",
        "message": "An unexpected error occurred",
        "requestId": "..."
    }
}
